<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Upper surface of sterile branch leaves of Chrysosplenium ramosissimum (A 1) and C. valdepilosum (B 1). Scanning electron micrograph of seeds of C. ramosissimum (A 2) and C. valdepilosum (B 2)." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.111.27182.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/240891" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">3</figureCitation>
